        public static int hashCode(IStatementPattern stmt)
        The hash code of a statement is defined as: 961 * subject.hashCode() + 31 * predicate.hashCode() + object.hashCode() + 29791 * context.hashCode() This is similar to how String.hashCode() is defined.
